description:
Every burgeoning artist has to do a few things to advance in the business: regularly practice their art, work as an apprentice under a more talented and published artist, draw nude models to get form and function down… but Hiroshi never thought he would be the nude model! Hiroshi’s working for Miki Orihara, a popular manga-ka, and his job entails everything from drawing backgrounds, practicing forms, and stripping down! He may not be getting the lessons he want, but he’s the canvas that Miki and her fellow staff will paint his wildest dreams on.
